{
  "texts": [
    "Converting genomic data files and tidying operations were also highlighted as demanding by a few participants (P6, P3, P15).",
    "Conversion was often needed to move data between tools.",
    "One participant reflected on the lack of support in this task: \"There's very common patterns that people keep coding themselves [...].",
    "That could be a thing to have [support for] [...] People often take this type of data and convert it to this [tidy data].\"",
    "(P6).Customizations and Aesthetics."
  ]
}